a.n: Trouble X 2: Abigai lMac & Ryan Driller

p.k: On his first day back in the dating game, Nick meets not one but TWO beautiful women. Olivia (Abigail Mac) is hot, sexy, and confident. Jenny (Cherie DeVille) is sweet, smart and funny. Not in a rush, he takes his time casually dating them both. Finally Nick knows he must make a choice.
